    description: 'Gidney and Ekerå publish a comprehensive compilation framework factoring 2048-bit RSA. <strong>Contribution:</strong> Provided the gold standard blueprint for scaling attack circuits, proving that an attack takes just 8 hours using 20 million noisy physical qubits in a Surface Code.'
