    description: 'Researchers demonstrate breaking secp256k1 using ≤ 1,200 logical qubits and ≤ 90 million Toffoli gates. <strong>Contribution:</strong> By integrating qLDPC codes and aggressive modular-arithmetic compression, the physical qubit overhead was slashed to under 500,000, drastically shifting the CRQC timeline.'
